room_title: Escape room "Prison Redemption" by Adventure Vault in Miami
room_address: 3350 NW 2nd Ave Suite A4, Boca Raton, FL 33431
room_description: You and your crew were framed for multiple bank robberies and sentenced to 50 years in prison! Your lawyers were unable to prove your innocence... You must take it upon yourself to escape the holding cell and find out where the next bank robbery will occur! Can you find out who's behind this, or will you go down for them?
